<div class="container mx-auto prose-xl">
    {{> 'partials/title_heading' title="Watch Our Congress! Help Keep Them Clean and Accountable!" }}


    <p>
        Congress travels a lot to support various initiatives and be informated on topics.
        We the people must watch and understand what these initiatives are and why they are traveling.
    </p>
    <p>
        Inform yourself below with filters on where they are traveling and who is sponsoring it.
    </p>

</div>

<hr />

<div class="container mx-auto prose-xl mt-12">
    <h2>Explore Congressional Hearings</h2>
    <p>
        Stay informed about the discussions and witness testimonies that shape our legislative landscape. 
        We have indexed <strong>{{ TotalHearings }}</strong> hearings held between <strong>{{ OldestHearing }}</strong> and <strong>{{ LatestHearing }}</strong> 
        across all House and Senate committees.
    </p>
    <p>
        Our platform provides you with direct access to full transcripts and official records, allowing you to 
        search and analyze the conversations that matter most in the 119th Congress and beyond.
    </p>
    <p>
        <a href="/hearings" class="btn no-underline">View All Hearings</a>
    </p>
</div>

<div class="container mx-auto prose-xl mt-12">
    <hr />
    <h2>Find out about recent gifted travel</h2>
    <div hx-get="/htmx/travel-gauge-cluster" hx-trigger="load"></div>
    <p>
        Find out about the most recent travel that has been gifted to our congress members. This is a great way to see
        who is
        influencing our congress members and how they are being influenced.
    </p>

    <div class="overflow-auto">
        <div hx-get="/htmx/recent-gift-travel" hx-trigger="load"></div>
    </div>
</div>


